{"type": "article", "id": 1979, "title": "一个士兵的装备演变", "description": "Best On The Web 是一个推荐性栏目，每个工作日我们会从互联网世界中找出最好看的内容，希望这个栏目让我们始终与阅读、知识和美好在一起。", "date": "2014-08-22T08:59:47Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 153, "name": "摄影"}, {"id": 2224, "name": "战争"}, {"id": 2531, "name": "士兵"}], "category": 12, "column": null, "author": 13, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060423062030OUT5rGHtE6xWQF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t在摄影师<a href=\"http://thomatkinson.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\"> Thom Atkinson</a> 的<a href=\"http://www.creativereview.co.uk/cr-blog/2014/august/thom-atkinson-soldiers-inventories\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\">镜头</a>下，你可以看到从黑斯廷斯战役至今一个士兵的装备演变——包括服装、武器和其它用品。Atkinson 接下来还会继续通过对战争的聚焦，关注英国文化当中如何呈现冲突。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这些「静物」以一种还原现场的方式呈现，似乎可以重现当时的部分情境——虽然是冷酷的器物，却也能看到人的影响和作用。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t每张照片都是对英国历史的截图。Atkinson 为此做了大量功课，来寻找能够代表当时时代特征的典型士兵的装束。最终，包括福克兰群岛战争的很多著名战役的装备，都建立在神话传说和想象之上。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t「英国历史似乎就是由一系列战争组成，它们非常感性。」在搜集过程中，令 Atkinson 最触动的体验是与一些为他提供过阿富汗照片的士兵的接触，「直到那一刻发生之前一切都显得非常不真实，但我所见到的他们就像是想象中那些历史中的士兵。」\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t当你看到下面这些照片的时候，不难想象，那些设计和摆布的过程，的确像「一点点在完成一幅拼图」。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230617HNan6oO0cpkG4Rmf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><em>Huscarl, Battle of Hastings, 1066</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><em> </em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134837JVRDazCZyq63S8F7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em><em>Mounted Knight, Siege of Jerusalem, 1244</em><em></em> </em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060423061861ns9WJqvjCwFSKZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><em>Yorkist Man at Arms, Battle of Bosworth, 1485</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230618qeb3YXxzruLm47ds.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><em>New Model Army Musketeer, Battle of Naseby, 1645</em><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230619FCY2Iga4qXSVhji0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><em>Private Soldier, Battle of Waterloo, 1815</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230619goVfx8iRSFCmJuZY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><em>Lance Corporal, Parachute Brigade, Battle of Arnhem, 1944</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230620edZO6aXFvYt0JjsH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><em>Close Support Sapper, Royal Engineers, Helmand Province, 2014</em><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}